    <briefdescription>
<para>Sequential binary writer for serializing message fields. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Writes values contiguously into a pre-allocated byte buffer. Strings are length-prefixed (uint32_t). Trivially copyable types are written via memcpy.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classconduit_1_1ReadBuffer" kindref="compound">ReadBuffer</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
